      "widgets_values": [
        "With this custom node, you can preview a 3 shot sequence quickly with Sora. You may choose an LLM provider or use CLIP or Qwen3VL locally if you have a sufficient GPU. If using an LLM, make sure to add your API key first.\n\nAdd a prompt for general style, optionally your subject, as well as descriptions of what is happening in each of your 3 scenes. You can then choose from different configurations from the dropdowns for each shot.\n\nBy default, you have options in the dropdown to set different parameters for each shot, and you can set up to 3 shots total. Use the toggles per shot to decide whether you want to use the presets or input images to drive each value. Image inputs will appear when toggled on, simply add a \"Load Image\" node to each.\n\nAdditionally, there is an override for lighting direction for each shot if you need."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
